     Danni, who also split with her boyfriend earlier this year, looked fantastic as she took a dip in the ocean and went for a bike ride by the beach. The star sported a black string bikini with a high waist which showcased her phenomenal figure as she enjoyed a day by the sea with some pals. The Scottish native accessorised with a simple necklace, bracelets and a pair of sunglasses. She wore her hair loose and added a black cap to protect her eyes from the sun as she cycled away from the beach.   